snippet: William Bennett, the principal oboist of the San Francisco Symphony, died on Thursday, the orchestra announced.
abstract: William Bennett, principal oboist of San Francisco Symphony, dies after suffering a brain hemorrhage and collapsing during a performance.
lead_paragraph: William Bennett, the principal oboist of the San Francisco Symphony, died on Thursday, the orchestra announced.

headline.main: San Francisco Symphony Oboist Who Collapsed Onstage Dies
